---
title: Mexican Chicken & Brown Rice Bowls with Pico de Gallo & Lime Sour Cream
description: The beauty of a bowl-style dinner is the DIY element. This meal begins with aromatic yellow rice and Southwest-spiced chicken, all jazzed up with pico de gallo and a limey crema. When ready to build your bowl, feel free to go crazy with assembly. Crema on bottom! Rice on top of chicken! Hot sauce on everything!!
